{"tid":1293854,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我希望\"成立獨立調查委員會追究黑警\"成為首要目標！","createTime":"2019-07-07T17:00:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T17:32:10.000Z","uid":12354,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5d5f01fc06cbb1c366ee67f21b408e951b61132d","tid":1293854,"uid":12354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:00:57.000Z","msg":"而家呢個局面，根本警隊已經成為咗政府嘅傀儡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當市民繼續屌柒差佬，差佬對上街嘅民眾怨恨又會再提升，將公義忘記得一清二楚！<br />\n<br />\n久而久之，淋病政府就獲得漁人之利，有一班政治傀儡幫佢出手清理市民。<br />\n輿論壓力就會落咗班死差佬度，警民關係持續惡化，陷入一個惡性循環！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地而家嘅首要目標必需要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">盡量放大一切黑警濫權事</span></span>件，得到國際社會關注，用輿論壓力逼使政府成立成立獨立機構，清洗警隊瘀血，令政府失去扯線公仔壓逼市民！"},{"pid":"5b2d70bae4050da8d9f1b01baab8cf2870c19d15","tid":1293854,"uid":12354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:01:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65849908ca71e55fe777613612686cbb303f6fdf","tid":1293854,"uid":12354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:02:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3a9a7bd03f83ac089bdff179170b7be2505cb8e","tid":1293854,"uid":43663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:03:06.000Z","msg":"其實政府唔肯做 民間可唔可以自發組織<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8d8146a7dbda36b7d79c24e1e38dbc0b912c84a","tid":1293854,"uid":12354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3a9a7bd03f83ac089bdff179170b7be2505cb8e","tid":1293854,"uid":43663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:03:06.000Z","msg":"其實政府唔肯做 民間可唔可以自發組織<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T17:05:58.000Z","msg":"民間組織只能夠做到證據搜集嗰部分，始終冇權力去治罪或作出懲罰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25100e385feca8367f493fccffffc295326618cb","tid":129385